Whiskey Sour:
- 2 oz bourbon whiskey
- 3/4 oz fresh lemon juice
- 1/2 oz simple syrup
- Garnish: Lemon wedge

Margarita:
- 2 oz tequila
- 1 oz lime juice
- 1/2 oz triple sec
- Garnish: Lime wheel

Martini:
- 2 1/2 oz gin
- 1/2 oz dry vermouth
- Garnish: Olive or twist of lemon peel

Old Fashioned:
- 2 oz bourbon whiskey
- 1/2 oz simple syrup
- 2 dashes Angostura bitters
- Garnish: Orange slice and cherry

Negroni:
- 1 oz gin
- 1 oz sweet vermouth
- 1 oz Campari
- Garnish: Orange peel

